{{Quote|Ah. Aha, crystal ferns. I have heard of them in other asteroids. Some prospectors search for them. They are quite fragile and therefore are considered great treasures.|[[Tenel Ka Djo]]|<ref name="Young Jedi Knights: Shards of Alderaan">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Shards of Alderaan]]''</ref>}}
'''Crystal ferns''' were plants believed by some to be primitive [[Silicon/Legends|silicon]]-based life-forms. The fern could be found in the [[Hoth asteroid field/Legends|Hoth asteroid field]]. It could grow up to several meters in height and propagated when shards of crystal were broken off and took hold on another asteroid.

